Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.23,0:02:06.16,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hey, Kitamura-kun. I was about to-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening to me, you stupid dog?!
