Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:04:01.84,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,A cellphone decoration? You're really dexterous with your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:07.57,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that. I might not look it, but I'm rather crafty with my hands.{repeat of the phrase above, but changed the wording. minorin's crafty with her fingers (since she decorates phones)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's Kushieda doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:15.80,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,All right, one down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.90,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that smothered voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Um, y-you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.95,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't I decorate yours too, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:36.59,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm a part-time cellphone decorator.{artisan or craftsman, whichever works for someone who does artsy shit to decorate stuff}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,D-Decorator?{same as above}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:41.45,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spell out "Ryuuji" with purple Swarovski stones on yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.88,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She'd do that for me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I-I'm all rig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:53.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please decorate ours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.98,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I see, more orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.71,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,On this paper, write down your name, the color you want, and a small drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:08.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,To give it a lovely feeling, I'll go with a large heart and the color pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.30,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:16.02,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So she's a part-time cellphone decorator...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:23.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The sparkling Kushieda and her sparkling\Ndecorations. What a wonderful combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:30.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Hey, Yacchan's not eating here since she's at the hostess club, right? Then can I have her side dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:34.25,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And she said "Ryuuji." She remembered my first name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.44,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I address you like that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, about Yacchan's side dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I talked with her so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, was I able to talk normally with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:45.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,...her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Listen when people are talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:56.37,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And no, you sounded really shady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.75,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What about dinner, is it ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you know! It's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:04.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we're having a rice bowl dish, so as long as we have rice we'll be ok-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,The rice cooker's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.11,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome and good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.85,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Going all the way out to a family restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have any rice, but there was bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.92,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Bay while you can, mongrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:31.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, you'll be kneeling your head in gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:35.31,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And here you go, two servings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:38.34,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But we haven't ordered anyth-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:39.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:45.42,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this a secret. An extra large serving of ice cream, the Taiga Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.01,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hide it from the other customers while you eat it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.76,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for making it every time, Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:52.84,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"Every time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.83,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun doesn't like sweet things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.28,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about some french fries?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:02.01,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a huge serving! A {\i1}huge{\i0}  serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:03.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:08.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin also works part time at places like\Nconvenience stores and karaoke clubs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:12.32,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And last week, I added a shabu-shabu place to the list!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.80,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm still saving time for other things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:21.00,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Being the girls' softball club's captain, I can't possibly skip club activities, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:24.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working so hard because you want something in particular?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:27.96,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I've just got the time so I gotta labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,"Labor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:32.09,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the "Mysterious Files of Labor"!{TL notes time, this is a pun-reference to the '96 show Ginrou Kaiki Files}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.83,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The kind of labor that revives you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:41.11,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,But, wow, you two sure are close now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.48,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Waitress, some cold water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.07,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, enjoy your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:07.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I've lost some eyesight because you've been poking my eyes all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:12.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You pitiful mongrel, drooling while checking out Minorin's uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,...that her smile was so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.52,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sp-Spare my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If I continue, my fingers will be contaminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:34.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But why is she juggling all those jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.76,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,She called it the "Mysterious Files of Labor", didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:42.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be possible that she has a reason for earning all that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:46.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Something related to her home? Maybe she's helping her sick mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,She called it laboring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:55.85,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop assuming things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:56.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm the only one who truly understands her!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.47,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only add on to your filth level.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:08.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ew, how gross! Keep your distance from me, you're so disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:14.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga! What's with your tone, you're so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:19.88,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me! Since when have I {\i1}not{\i0}  been cold towards you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:27.54,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Inko-chan! Sorry to make you wait, it's dinner time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a huge serving! A {\i1}huge{\i0}  serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:35.73,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,-nko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:38.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, today you'll be able to say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.18,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,-nko, -oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.14,Default,Inko-chan,0000,0000,0000,,Poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:10:00.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the mornings during holidays are really refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:04.19,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:10.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Not bothering to prepare breakfast in order to see Minorin at the family restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:14.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, the rice cooker is still broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we go to an electrical appliance store first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.84,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You even said you hate bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind eating bread for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:26.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so cheerful? Those clothes don't look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot something at home-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:29.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What you wear won't make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.83,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.34,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you Mirano-chan's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, old man Inage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,"Mirano"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.88,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Yasuko's hostess name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:56.84,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Go out the station's north exit, it's 200 meters straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.52,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Vaisravana's Heaven's Mirano-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.92,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,How old do I look? Twenty-three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.26,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.44,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fortunate morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:13.02,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,And now to grab a feel of Mirano-chan's DNA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:17.23,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Nice and firm, being young must be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:22.29,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, this old guy's pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.49,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, you two! If you haven't eaten breakfast yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:30.33,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend the docosahexaenoic acid and the calcium-filled taste of this Gyonisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:38.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.88,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Here, carry this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:46.79,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Another!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.89,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,And some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better if I-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:58.83,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. Sit down and relax with some tea. You're Mirano-chan's son, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:03.89,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:07.83,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,I ask her for some help, but only during holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.34,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, you better work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.33,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:17.79,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,We've run out of workers these days, now that we're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You ran out of workers...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:24.72,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, do you want to work here too, young lady? Being friends with Kushieda and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.59,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.56,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.68,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:49.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't cause a ruckus. It'll give Kushieda trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:52.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then help out a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.00,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl, I need you to go do the deliveries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.39,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Three of those beer cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.38,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,And that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:14.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:22.65,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You can't ride a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:34.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I can't ride a bike?! I'll just have to transport it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong! You're doing it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.04,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You're on fire, Taiga!{literally Minorin's saying that stuff's spurting from Taiga??}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:48.01,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if she just pushes the bike, she'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:51.45,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I was going to restock the shochu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:03.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad if I wasn't doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.54,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.13,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the potato shochu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's really hard to see in this darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:33.51,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,This place isn't used that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.48,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,They don't open up this place more than once a week or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.73,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,If we got locked in here, it'd be horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.84,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It would feel almost like we were stranded or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:50.81,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,That little runt, leaving it open like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:59.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There are still people inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,S.O.S.! S.O.S.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.19,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:06.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.67,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's for these times that we have school songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:10.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:12.97,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,School songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:39.08,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This is dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:42.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for me to make an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:46.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.94,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Keep what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:56.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kitamura-kun! W-Why are you h-h-here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:58.13,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Self-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.62,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, is that your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:08.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah... something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.76,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You're capable of riding a bike now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:14.63,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's remarkable progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:19.43,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, putting aside whether I can ride a bike or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:26.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that I didn't know how to ride a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:31.59,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I was closely observing you last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:37.06,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Bikes are great. The world opens up before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.98,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.83,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,He was observing me last year...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:02.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.59,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:15.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Opening up a world in which\NKitamura-kun's not watching me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:24.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,...is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.98,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Two, thr-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:36.39,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lat- What happened, you look awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:39.25,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much. Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.29,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, where has that Kushieda run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.98,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Not minding Ryuuji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That mongrel, slacking off in comfort while I'm out working!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.59,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.55,Default,Cabbage,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the next delivery's three blocks away-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:01.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, what the hell are you up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:10.21,Default,Ryuuji & Minori,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The bridge that leads to the future ♫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:14.04,Default,Ryuuji & Minori,0000,0000,0000,,♫ That bridge is a chopstick, a chopstick ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.03,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,My throat's all dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:20.38,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody noticed us even though we raised our voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:24.09,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,At around this time, the old guy's obsessing over horse racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.40,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.67,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten a bit cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:29.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you my coat, the-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.50,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:38.00,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:41.73,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:44.14,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Who's scared? Aren't you the pitcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.63,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,He's scared! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.60,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,He's scared! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:49.19,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:53.00,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,The pitcher is scared! Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:54.32,Alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're actually scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:57.67,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your hand's trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:01.97,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong, I'm trembling from excitement!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.16,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, you'd better be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.02,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.08,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Changeover.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.68,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,We swap places now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.77,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.95,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You see, there's no point being afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.00,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:25.41,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I only need to beat up my weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.60,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.33,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:37.39,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu-kun. Can't we get out through that window?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:45.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?! Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.63,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,WHERE IS HE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.92,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So you're in there...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:20:04.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,There might be more to Kushieda's cheerfulness than her simply being bright and energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.22,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kushieda! Are you oka-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.05,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, your nose is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:16.40,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it'll be okay somewhy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.15,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,A nosebleed is the perspiration of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.25,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.89,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Keep stacking them boxes, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:25.88,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:31.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see, she was beating up her weakness, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get out of here!{literally, he's using a baseball term for returning to your home base, which also can be used for surviving in a jungle and return home from like, uh, a planecrash. being liberal.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.39,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:39.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.24,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,When I say fight, you say...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.70,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chug one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.09,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.70,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,C-Chug one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.87,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.37,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,she's always been gleaming with cheerfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:55.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I had just met her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.69,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:58.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Chug one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,She's gleaming with joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:09.78,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOU{\alpha&HFF&}ND YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:10.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOUND {\alpha&HFF&}YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOUND YO{\alpha&HFF&}U!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:13.45,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,FOUND YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:28.15,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, how did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.39,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,How? I used the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:35.07,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We can get outside now, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:37.46,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.66,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly the ladder to the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:40.78,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:42.63,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,You get up too, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:45.18,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The ladder fell down when I landed on Ryuuji's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:26.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0010,,Sealed deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:29.38,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0010,,Our precious memory that we couldn't tell anyone about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:31.69,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0010,,Nope, I've told Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:34.18,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0010,,Ki-ta-mu-!
Comment: 0,0:13:30.91,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪♫
